social_posts.post_text: Tomorrow night at @eddiesattic will be a special one as we will be recording this show!  The awesomely talented @ansleedavidsonmusic opens up at 9PM sharp. Few tickets/tables still available via the link in my bio!

Love and am so grateful for my 4 Valentine’s!  Number one mama, @annat_dodd you’re the absolute best! ❤️

As songwriters, we study the craft, we study how the best do it and today, I had the honor of writing with one of the GOAT to ever put pen to paper. We love what we do for so many reasons and strive to get that next level - so awesome seeing a master at work. Enjoyed it very much @tomdouglasmusic !  Always a blast @blakegriffithmusic @cjsolar !  Keep on dreaming, y’all !
HAPPY NUMBER ONE to Parker!  You’ve made life as good as it gets for so many!  Love you so much, and know that your MA-MA and I are so proud of you!
